572
00:19:06,460 --> 00:19:08,260
People see your politeness
as a blessing.

573
00:19:09,320 --> 00:19:10,940
You need to know where to draw the line.

574
00:19:10,940 --> 00:19:12,420
Why haven't you learned?

575
00:19:13,860 --> 00:19:15,700
We are here to discuss your marriage

576
00:19:15,700 --> 00:19:16,580
but you came out

577
00:19:16,580 --> 00:19:18,340
to play with children.

578
00:19:19,420 --> 00:19:20,140
Come inside.

579
00:19:20,260 --> 00:19:22,420
What will happen
when Mingzhu marries into his family?

580
00:19:22,420 --> 00:19:23,940
This mother-in-law is hard to please.

581
00:19:23,940 --> 00:19:24,820
She's quite fierce.

582
00:19:25,060 --> 00:19:26,380
Mingzhu will suffer

583
00:19:26,720 --> 00:19:27,540
in the future.

584
00:19:28,100 --> 00:19:29,140
Cheers.

585
00:19:33,300 --> 00:19:34,460
I'm fine. I'm happy today.

586
00:19:34,940 --> 00:19:35,660
Mr. Shen,

587
00:19:37,340 --> 00:19:38,460
we are here

588
00:19:38,700 --> 00:19:40,180
to discuss

589
00:19:40,300 --> 00:19:41,460
our children's marriage.

590
00:19:42,380 --> 00:19:44,660
Our children's marriage
is a joyous occasion.

591
00:19:45,060 --> 00:19:46,300
So, the wedding

592
00:19:46,300 --> 00:19:47,700
must be organized

593
00:19:47,820 --> 00:19:49,740
with splendor.

594
00:19:49,740 --> 00:19:50,940
Absolutely.

595
00:19:50,940 --> 00:19:53,580
A wedding must feel ceremonial.

596
00:19:53,580 --> 00:19:54,500
That's right.

597
00:19:54,740 --> 00:19:55,620
It must be ceremonial.

598
00:19:56,420 --> 00:19:58,180
Whatever you think is suitable,

599
00:19:58,340 --> 00:19:59,580
we will follow suit.

600
00:20:00,260 --> 00:20:01,020
That's right.

601
00:20:01,180 --> 00:20:02,660
As long as it's best for the children,

602
00:20:02,940 --> 00:20:04,020
we are fine with anything.

603
00:20:04,020 --> 00:20:05,020
We are fine.

604
00:20:05,020 --> 00:20:05,980
All right.

605
00:20:06,260 --> 00:20:07,220
It's like this.

606
00:20:07,780 --> 00:20:08,860
We want

607
00:20:08,860 --> 00:20:11,580
to organize the wedding at Lijun Hotel.

608
00:20:12,100 --> 00:20:13,900
There's a dome in their banquet hall.

609
00:20:13,900 --> 00:20:14,900
It's very majestic.

610
00:20:16,340 --> 00:20:17,780
It can fit 100 tables.

611
00:20:18,460 --> 00:20:19,580
That's too expensive.

612
00:20:19,580 --> 00:20:21,420
- You'll be paying a lot of money.
- Not at all.

613
00:20:21,420 --> 00:20:22,580
A little expensive is fine.

614
00:20:23,020 --> 00:20:23,980
We make money as parents

615
00:20:23,980 --> 00:20:25,380
for the sake of our children.

616
00:20:25,700 --> 00:20:26,260
Yes.

617
00:20:26,660 --> 00:20:27,820
You are right.

618
00:20:27,820 --> 00:20:28,900
It's for our children.

619
00:20:28,900 --> 00:20:29,460
Yes.

620
00:20:29,860 --> 00:20:32,580
How many tables
are you going to organize?

621
00:20:33,540 --> 00:20:36,220
We made a rough calculation.

622
00:20:36,820 --> 00:20:38,060
Basically, our family

623
00:20:38,060 --> 00:20:39,740
has been doing business for a long time

624
00:20:39,740 --> 00:20:41,100
so we know more people.

625
00:20:41,460 --> 00:20:42,460
There are many

626
00:20:42,460 --> 00:20:45,340
40 tables might not be enough.

627
00:20:45,340 --> 00:20:46,460
Yes. That's a must.

628
00:20:46,700 --> 00:20:47,660
That's necessary.

629
00:20:47,820 --> 00:20:50,180
All of you know many people.

630
00:20:50,340 --> 00:20:50,820
Right?

631
00:20:51,100 --> 00:20:53,060
It's normal to have 40 to 50 tables.

632
00:20:53,060 --> 00:20:53,780
That's right.

633
00:20:53,780 --> 00:20:54,740
The more guests,

634
00:20:54,740 --> 00:20:56,060
the more festive it is.

635
00:20:56,060 --> 00:20:57,380
We doesn't have
that many guests.

636
00:20:57,380 --> 00:20:58,540
Just ten tables.

637
00:21:00,020 --> 00:21:01,100
Didn't we agree

638
00:21:01,100 --> 00:21:02,980
to have at least 15 tables?

639
00:21:03,860 --> 00:21:04,940
Do we have that many people?

640
00:21:05,100 --> 00:21:07,460
No. Mrs. Shen.

641
00:21:08,060 --> 00:21:09,500
Mr. Shen.

642
00:21:09,500 --> 00:21:10,060
To save money.

643
00:21:11,340 --> 00:21:11,780
Go ahead.

644
00:21:13,860 --> 00:21:16,380
We have a request to ask.

645
00:21:16,380 --> 00:21:17,540
What do you mean?

646
00:21:17,900 --> 00:21:19,780
Don't be offended by this.

647
00:21:20,500 --> 00:21:21,700
Why should we?

648
00:21:21,700 --> 00:21:23,580
We are discussing the wedding.

649
00:21:23,580 --> 00:21:25,620
There's nothing
to feel offended about. Say it.

650
00:21:25,620 --> 00:21:26,420
It's for them.

651
00:21:26,420 --> 00:21:27,180
That's great.

652
00:21:27,780 --> 00:21:29,220
Well...

653
00:21:29,780 --> 00:21:31,540
Fine, I'll say it.

654
00:21:33,300 --> 00:21:34,060
It's like this.

655
00:21:34,460 --> 00:21:35,300
We have decided

656
00:21:37,060 --> 00:21:38,700
to hold our own weddings.

657
00:21:41,300 --> 00:21:42,660
The groom's side

658
00:21:42,900 --> 00:21:44,260
will be held at Lijun Hotel.

659
00:21:44,660 --> 00:21:45,500
During the wedding,

660
00:21:45,500 --> 00:21:47,580
guests from the bride's side
do not have to attend.

661
00:21:48,460 --> 00:21:49,900
It's too far

662
00:21:49,900 --> 00:21:50,840
and it's inconvenient.

663
00:21:51,460 --> 00:21:54,100
All of you can hold the banquet

664
00:21:54,100 --> 00:21:55,060
at a nearby hotel.

665
00:21:59,260 --> 00:22:01,100
It's like this?

666
00:22:01,100 --> 00:22:02,260
We hold our own weddings?

667
00:22:02,460 --> 00:22:03,180
Well...

668
00:22:03,340 --> 00:22:04,940
It's still quite reasonable.

669
00:22:04,940 --> 00:22:05,780
Exactly.

670
00:22:05,940 --> 00:22:06,980
Mr. Feng. Mrs. Feng.

671
00:22:07,580 --> 00:22:09,580
I think that's not quite right.

672
00:22:09,580 --> 00:22:10,620
No.

673
00:22:11,380 --> 00:22:12,500
It's not right at all.

674
00:22:12,500 --> 00:22:14,020
What do you mean?

675
00:22:14,020 --> 00:22:15,180
I think it's right.

676
00:22:15,180 --> 00:22:16,940
Your parents have agreed.

677
00:22:16,940 --> 00:22:18,020
Of course, it's not.

678
00:22:18,620 --> 00:22:20,060
If my parents are not going,

679
00:22:20,620 --> 00:22:21,740
my sister shouldn't go.

680
00:22:21,800 --> 00:22:23,460
Just get Feng Jianqi
to attend on his own.

681
00:22:23,460 --> 00:22:24,820
Shen Minghui, shut up.

682
00:22:24,820 --> 00:22:26,060
The child is speaking nonsense.

683
00:22:26,060 --> 00:22:27,140
Apologize, hurry.

684
00:22:27,140 --> 00:22:28,300
Why should I apologize, Mom?

685
00:22:28,820 --> 00:22:30,660
They are obviously
looking down on our family.

686
00:22:31,060 --> 00:22:32,340
Why should we apologize?

687
00:22:32,340 --> 00:22:33,260
Stand up.

688
00:22:33,260 --> 00:22:34,620
Mom, I'm not going back.

689
00:22:35,210 --> 00:22:35,780
If I go back,

690
00:22:35,780 --> 00:22:37,260
Mingzhu will be badly bullied.

691
00:22:37,900 --> 00:22:38,860
Minghui, calm down.

692
00:22:38,860 --> 00:22:39,660
Me?

693
00:22:40,020 --> 00:22:41,540
Has your family spoken politely?

694
00:22:41,780 --> 00:22:44,580
The more polite our family is,
the more your family tries to bully us.

695
00:22:44,580 --> 00:22:45,700
Don't point at others.

696
00:22:46,220 --> 00:22:47,420
My sister is getting married.

697
00:22:47,540 --> 00:22:49,060
Why can't my family attend her wedding?

698
00:22:49,450 --> 00:22:50,940
Just because it's held at Lijun Hotel?

699
00:22:51,140 --> 00:22:52,740
Is Lijun Hotel owned by your family?

700
00:22:53,300 --> 00:22:54,380
Is there a lock or a curfew?

701
00:22:54,380 --> 00:22:54,980
Shen Minghui!

702
00:22:54,980 --> 00:22:56,180
Are you going to stop every guest
who is not from the Feng family?

703
00:22:56,180 --> 00:22:56,860
Shen Minghui!

704
00:22:56,860 --> 00:22:58,300
Listen to me. Let's go back.

705
00:22:58,300 --> 00:22:59,700
You are so uneducated.

706
00:23:01,500 --> 00:23:03,260
The wedding can be cancelled

707
00:23:03,700 --> 00:23:05,140
but your sister is pregnant.

708
00:23:05,380 --> 00:23:06,260
Just cancel it!

709
00:23:06,560 --> 00:23:07,860
Many people are after my sister!

710
00:23:07,860 --> 00:23:08,860
Just find someone else!

711
00:23:08,870 --> 00:23:10,500
The child
will call someone else his father!

712
00:23:10,500 --> 00:23:10,980
Shen Minghui.

713
00:23:10,980 --> 00:23:11,740
What are you talking about?

714
00:23:11,740 --> 00:23:13,140
- Don't touch me!
- I'll beat you up!

715
00:23:13,140 --> 00:23:14,500
Jianqi!

716
00:23:14,820 --> 00:23:15,580
Are you all right?

717
00:23:17,060 --> 00:23:17,820
You are bleeding.

718
00:23:17,820 --> 00:23:18,580
Go upstairs!

719
00:23:18,780 --> 00:23:20,580
Why did you hit him?

720
00:23:20,590 --> 00:23:22,020
- Why did you hit him?
- Are you all right?

721
00:23:22,020 --> 00:23:22,700
I'm fine.

722
00:23:22,700 --> 00:23:23,740
Jianqi, you are bleeding.

723
00:23:23,740 --> 00:23:24,260
Are you all right?

724
00:23:24,260 --> 00:23:24,940
Who are you?

725
00:23:24,940 --> 00:23:26,180
Why did you hit him?

726
00:23:26,300 --> 00:23:26,980
Jianqi!

727
00:23:26,980 --> 00:23:28,080
Come home with me.

728
00:23:28,080 --> 00:23:29,580
We don't want that child. Divorce her!

729
00:23:29,580 --> 00:23:31,460
- Mom.
- Mrs. Feng, what are you saying?

730
00:23:31,460 --> 00:23:33,580
Who are you calling? I don't know you!
Don't address me.

731
00:23:33,580 --> 00:23:35,180
I don't know you. It's all your fault.

732
00:23:35,180 --> 00:23:36,500
Is that how you talk?

733
00:23:36,500 --> 00:23:37,140
Stop talking.

734
00:23:37,140 --> 00:23:37,580
Mrs. Feng.

735
00:23:37,580 --> 00:23:38,540
Come home with me.

736
00:23:38,540 --> 00:23:39,300
No.

737
00:23:39,300 --> 00:23:40,220
I'll ask you again.

738
00:23:40,220 --> 00:23:41,260
Come home with me.

739
00:23:41,420 --> 00:23:42,060
No!

740
00:23:42,060 --> 00:23:43,140
Fine.

741
00:23:43,140 --> 00:23:44,100
Just stay here!

742
00:23:44,100 --> 00:23:45,380
Stay here!

743
00:23:45,380 --> 00:23:45,940
Let's go!

744
00:23:45,940 --> 00:23:47,660
Why are you so uneducated?

745
00:23:47,660 --> 00:23:48,100
That's enough.

746
00:23:48,100 --> 00:23:50,220
I've never seen a mother like you!

747
00:23:50,220 --> 00:23:51,940
I've been holding back
the entire morning!

748
00:23:51,940 --> 00:23:53,980
You are just a hag! Look at all of you!

749
00:23:53,980 --> 00:23:55,420
Who do you think you are?

750
00:23:55,420 --> 00:23:56,900
You're just pretending to be civilized!

751
00:23:56,900 --> 00:23:57,900
You are impossible!

752
00:23:57,900 --> 00:23:59,260
Enough! Stand right here!

753
00:23:59,260 --> 00:24:00,460
You are being unreasonable!

754
00:24:00,740 --> 00:24:01,620
Are you all right?

755
00:24:01,620 --> 00:24:03,020
Report to the police! We'll be waiting!

756
00:24:03,020 --> 00:24:04,500
Dad!

757
00:24:04,500 --> 00:24:05,220
Are you all right?

758
00:24:05,220 --> 00:24:06,660
I'm fine! Go back!

759
00:24:06,660 --> 00:24:07,740
They are so uncultured.

760
00:24:07,740 --> 00:24:08,380
I'm telling you.

761
00:24:08,380 --> 00:24:09,900
What kind of family is this?

762
00:24:09,910 --> 00:24:10,740
- Sorry.
- I'm telling you.

763
00:24:10,740 --> 00:24:11,820
I won't come back again.

764
00:24:11,820 --> 00:24:12,900
Let's go.

765
00:24:12,900 --> 00:24:13,740
What's happened?

766
00:24:13,740 --> 00:24:14,620
What's going on?

767
00:24:14,620 --> 00:24:15,980
- Exactly.
- That's too much.

768
00:24:15,980 --> 00:24:16,460
No.

769
00:24:16,460 --> 00:24:17,300
Mr. Feng!

770
00:24:17,500 --> 00:24:18,420
Shen has come out.

771
00:24:19,620 --> 00:24:21,380
The child...

772
00:24:22,540 --> 00:24:23,740
Feng.

773
00:24:24,060 --> 00:24:25,820
Don't take his words to heart.

774
00:24:25,820 --> 00:24:27,420
He's too reckless.

775
00:24:28,500 --> 00:24:29,060
Well...

776
00:24:29,060 --> 00:24:29,580
Quick.

777
00:24:29,580 --> 00:24:30,300
Make way.

778
00:24:30,300 --> 00:24:31,180
Why are they leaving?

779
00:24:31,180 --> 00:24:32,700
Sure. Don't be angry.

780
00:24:33,260 --> 00:24:34,380
Why are they angry?

781
00:24:34,380 --> 00:24:34,980
Well...

782
00:24:34,980 --> 00:24:36,140
What's wrong, Shen?

783
00:24:36,140 --> 00:24:37,300
What happened, Shen?

784
00:24:37,500 --> 00:24:39,380
Shen, what happened?

785
00:24:39,380 --> 00:24:40,340
What's going on?

786
00:24:40,340 --> 00:24:41,780
Shen, that was your in-laws.

787
00:24:46,700 --> 00:24:47,540
Time to eat!

788
00:24:48,453 --> 00:24:49,053
Come.

789
00:24:51,300 --> 00:24:51,980
Mom,

790
00:24:52,380 --> 00:24:53,960
if you agree to let me keep a puppy,

791
00:24:53,960 --> 00:24:55,860
I'll agree to you
giving birth to a second baby.

792
00:24:56,660 --> 00:24:57,700
Thanks a lot.

793
00:24:57,980 --> 00:24:58,940
You're welcome.

794
00:24:59,300 --> 00:25:00,780
The kind of dog Wang Ziqian has

795
00:25:00,780 --> 00:25:01,620
is good enough.

796
00:25:03,388 --> 00:25:05,410
I did my best to give birth
and raise my daughter.

797
00:25:05,700 --> 00:25:07,820
I brought her up

798
00:25:08,020 --> 00:25:09,900
just to let her ask me to keep a dog.

799
00:25:10,500 --> 00:25:11,700
I agree.

800
00:25:12,260 --> 00:25:13,380
I like dogs too.

801
00:25:13,380 --> 00:25:14,660
You are the best.

802
00:25:15,260 --> 00:25:16,460
Your father agrees.

803
00:25:16,470 --> 00:25:17,640
I'll leave if the dog is here.

804
00:25:19,820 --> 00:25:20,500
Jiao,

805
00:25:20,940 --> 00:25:23,180
your mother is right
not to let you keep a dog.

806
00:25:23,780 --> 00:25:26,420
Keeping a pet means taking responsibility
for its whole life.

807
00:25:26,420 --> 00:25:28,060
Before you are prepared for that,

808
00:25:28,060 --> 00:25:29,100
you should be careful.

809
00:25:29,100 --> 00:25:30,980
You are helping your wife instead of me.

810
00:25:30,980 --> 00:25:32,460
Of course, I'm helping my wife.

811
00:25:32,740 --> 00:25:34,540
My wife is our family's commander.

812
00:25:34,660 --> 00:25:35,660
That's right, Commander.

813
00:25:35,960 --> 00:25:37,820
Why are you always
comparing yourself to a dog?

814
00:25:39,700 --> 00:25:41,780
Is there a commander as sad as I am?

815
00:25:42,660 --> 00:25:43,660
No one in the family

816
00:25:43,660 --> 00:25:44,620
makes me feel relieved.

817
00:25:44,620 --> 00:25:46,020
I have to worry about them.

818
00:25:46,460 --> 00:25:49,060
I live worse than a dog
in my middle age.

819
00:25:50,740 --> 00:25:52,660
Wang Ziqian's dog even goes to a spa.

820
00:25:53,340 --> 00:25:55,540
When have I done that in my life?

821
00:25:55,860 --> 00:25:57,660
It costs 1,000 yuan once.

822
00:25:58,180 --> 00:25:59,660
I only paid 48 yuan for my haircut.

823
00:25:59,860 --> 00:26:01,140
I want to become Wang Ziqian.

824
00:26:02,500 --> 00:26:03,740
So, I can take care of you.

825
00:26:04,820 --> 00:26:06,060
I'm not as good as you.

826
00:26:06,380 --> 00:26:08,020
My haircut is only 15 yuan.

827
00:26:08,020 --> 00:26:09,950
Why are both of you
comparing yourselves to dogs?

828
00:26:17,180 --> 00:26:18,260
What are you thinking about?

829
00:26:19,540 --> 00:26:20,260
My mother

830
00:26:21,180 --> 00:26:23,580
is asking me to find
my younger sister again.

831
00:26:23,860 --> 00:26:24,780
How can I find her

832
00:26:24,780 --> 00:26:26,260
when there are so many people?

833
00:26:27,540 --> 00:26:29,700
I helped you post on the internet.

834
00:26:29,860 --> 00:26:31,660
It's like casting a huge net.

835
00:26:33,660 --> 00:26:34,860
Look at me.

836
00:26:36,060 --> 00:26:37,360
I have to take care of my husband

837
00:26:38,100 --> 00:26:39,260
and serve my child.

838
00:26:40,180 --> 00:26:41,140
I need to work.

839
00:26:42,160 --> 00:26:43,760
I also need to find my younger sister.

840
00:26:44,300 --> 00:26:46,140
I'm also pregnant with my second child.

841
00:26:47,418 --> 00:26:48,543
My life is so tough.

842
00:26:50,260 --> 00:26:51,900
Do you think I should give birth or not?

843
00:26:51,900 --> 00:26:53,340
Let's raise our hands to vote.

844
00:26:54,340 --> 00:26:55,380
I'm the first to agree.

845
00:26:57,040 --> 00:26:59,020
Are you going to agree
if she lets you keep a dog?

846
00:26:59,260 --> 00:27:00,890
That means
she has abstained from voting.

847
00:27:00,900 --> 00:27:01,820
I've decided.

848
00:27:02,020 --> 00:27:02,900
I agree as well.

849
00:27:04,460 --> 00:27:06,500
You change your mind so quickly.

850
00:27:06,700 --> 00:27:07,660
I've thought about it.

851
00:27:07,710 --> 00:27:10,180
If you give birth to another baby,
he wants to keep a dog too.

852
00:27:10,460 --> 00:27:11,660
Then, it'll be two against two.

853
00:27:12,300 --> 00:27:13,300
Ganging up now?

854
00:27:14,700 --> 00:27:16,500
Yes. We love you together.

855
00:27:17,420 --> 00:27:18,260
