00:38:02,860 --> 00:38:04,060
Take good care of Shen Mingzhu.

1138
00:38:05,220 --> 00:38:05,980
Is that so?

1139
00:38:07,060 --> 00:38:07,940
I came to you

1140
00:38:07,940 --> 00:38:08,900
to tell you

1141
00:38:09,380 --> 00:38:10,540
that you must thank Mr. Feng

1142
00:38:10,540 --> 00:38:12,220
when you go back.

1143
00:38:12,900 --> 00:38:13,780
One more thing.

1144
00:38:14,940 --> 00:38:16,180
If it's convenient,

1145
00:38:16,340 --> 00:38:17,700
help me put in a good word

1146
00:38:17,700 --> 00:38:19,820
to Mr. Feng about our hotel.

1147
00:38:20,940 --> 00:38:23,180
It's tough doing this business.

1148
00:38:23,380 --> 00:38:25,060
All the mid-level executives

1149
00:38:25,420 --> 00:38:26,780
are stressed about sales.

1150
00:38:26,780 --> 00:38:28,540
I understand. Don't worry.

1151
00:38:28,540 --> 00:38:30,820
I'll come to you for top-ups.

1152
00:38:31,340 --> 00:38:34,060
See? No wonder you can marry a rich man.

1153
00:38:34,340 --> 00:38:35,260
You have a high EQ.

1154
00:38:35,880 --> 00:38:36,940
I'll go back to work then.

1155
00:38:36,940 --> 00:38:37,540
Sure.

1156
00:38:38,020 --> 00:38:38,980
Rest more.

1157
00:38:38,980 --> 00:38:39,580
Sure.

1158
00:38:40,780 --> 00:38:41,940
Everyone is busy.

1159
00:38:42,660 --> 00:38:45,500
Is everyone eating lunchboxes again?

1160
00:38:45,860 --> 00:38:46,500
Yes.

1161
00:38:46,960 --> 00:38:47,980
I won't be ordering today.

1162
00:38:47,980 --> 00:38:49,140
I've prepared a feast.

1163
00:38:50,060 --> 00:38:51,460
A feast?

1164
00:38:59,260 --> 00:39:00,820
It's a feast indeed.

1165
00:39:01,420 --> 00:39:03,380
This is a good lunchbox.

1166
00:39:03,900 --> 00:39:05,380
My father-in-law opens a restaurant.

1167
00:39:05,380 --> 00:39:06,500
He prepared them for me.

1168
00:39:06,700 --> 00:39:08,300
I also want a father-in-law like him.

1169
00:39:08,620 --> 00:39:09,340
Count me in.

1170
00:39:09,820 --> 00:39:11,300
Sorry, you are late.

1171
00:39:11,860 --> 00:39:12,660
My father-in-law

1172
00:39:12,660 --> 00:39:14,340
only has one daughter.

1173
00:39:14,460 --> 00:39:15,700
She's Mrs. Feng now.

1174
00:39:16,660 --> 00:39:18,700
Feng married the daughter
of a restaurant owner.

1175
00:39:19,060 --> 00:39:20,140
Ever since,

1176
00:39:20,340 --> 00:39:22,100
he has achieved the pinnacle in life.

1177
00:39:23,180 --> 00:39:24,700
Let us try it as well.

1178
00:39:24,700 --> 00:39:25,620
Next time.

1179
00:39:25,860 --> 00:39:27,060
This is specially made

1180
00:39:27,060 --> 00:39:29,340
by my father-in-law.

1181
00:39:30,100 --> 00:39:31,580
Are you trying to tease us on purpose?

1182
00:39:34,700 --> 00:39:36,540
How is it? Is it delicious?

1183
00:39:43,340 --> 00:39:45,020
It's incredible.

1184
00:39:49,660 --> 00:39:50,700
(Forever in our memories )

1185
00:39:50,700 --> 00:39:52,020
Mom,

1186
00:39:52,300 --> 00:39:55,060
if you have any clues,

1187
00:39:55,500 --> 00:39:57,100
remember to tell me in my dreams.

1188
00:40:10,060 --> 00:40:10,780
Hello.

1189
00:40:12,140 --> 00:40:12,900
Yes.

1190
00:40:13,540 --> 00:40:15,060
Yes. We are looking for someone.

1191
00:40:15,060 --> 00:40:15,820
You are...

1192
00:40:19,980 --> 00:40:20,940
Our caretakers

1193
00:40:20,940 --> 00:40:22,300
are very experienced.

1194
00:40:22,580 --> 00:40:25,340
Our VIP wards and the delivery room
are combined.

1195
00:40:25,340 --> 00:40:26,780
We have constant temperature, humidity,
and also a constant level of care.

1196
00:40:26,780 --> 00:40:28,660
Our postpartum caregiver
is also working around the clock.

1197
00:40:28,660 --> 00:40:29,900
They can provide the utmost care

1198
00:40:29,900 --> 00:40:31,180
to the baby and his mother.

1199
00:40:31,940 --> 00:40:32,660
Well...

1200
00:40:32,660 --> 00:40:33,740
Can you give me

1201
00:40:33,740 --> 00:40:35,300
the premium pregnancy set's information

1202
00:40:35,300 --> 00:40:36,020
to me?

1203
00:40:36,020 --> 00:40:36,580
Sure.

1204
00:40:37,460 --> 00:40:38,100
Thank you.

1205
00:40:42,280 --> 00:40:43,980
Give me the information
on the premium abortion set

1206
00:40:43,980 --> 00:40:45,020
as well.

1207
00:40:45,860 --> 00:40:48,220
We don't need that.

1208
00:40:49,500 --> 00:40:50,740
Are you the one giving birth?

1209
00:40:54,580 --> 00:40:56,980
You'll give birth
and I'll raise the baby.

1210
00:41:01,140 --> 00:41:03,180
Get a bigger house for the baby then.

1211
00:41:05,900 --> 00:41:08,300
How is that related to this?

1212
00:41:08,900 --> 00:41:10,740
The baby is young.

1213
00:41:10,740 --> 00:41:11,820
He won't mind.

1214
00:41:12,140 --> 00:41:13,860
The big baby, Jiao, cares about that.

1215
00:41:14,620 --> 00:41:16,140
She needs her own space.

1216
00:41:17,100 --> 00:41:18,280
Why don't we do it like this?

1217
00:41:18,860 --> 00:41:20,580
You'll raise the child.

1218
00:41:20,820 --> 00:41:21,900
I'll take Jiao

1219
00:41:22,100 --> 00:41:22,820
and find her

1220
00:41:22,820 --> 00:41:24,620
a father who can provide us
with a big house.

1221
00:41:27,900 --> 00:41:29,380
Can you get me another glass of water?

1222
00:41:29,580 --> 00:41:30,220
Sure.

1223
00:41:32,820 --> 00:41:33,740
This has nothing to do

1224
00:41:33,740 --> 00:41:35,220
with finding a father

1225
00:41:35,220 --> 00:41:36,440
who can get her a bigger house?

1226
00:41:36,620 --> 00:41:37,820
Does Jiao need another father?

1227
00:41:37,820 --> 00:41:39,380
Jiao needs a dog.

1228
00:41:40,440 --> 00:41:41,820
Don't you need space to keep a dog?

1229
00:41:41,820 --> 00:41:42,380
You do.

1230
00:41:42,740 --> 00:41:45,060
I still need to find a father
who can get me a big house.

1231
00:41:45,060 --> 00:41:46,920
Why do you insist
on finding another father?

1232
00:41:48,480 --> 00:41:49,840
How about finding another mother?

1233
00:41:50,660 --> 00:41:52,020
I can't bear losing you.

1234
00:41:52,020 --> 00:41:52,980
I can't.

1235
00:41:56,580 --> 00:41:57,460
(Premium Abortion Set,
Premium Pregnancy Set)

1236
00:41:57,460 --> 00:42:00,540
See? Giving birth
and not giving birth are both expensive.

1237
00:42:01,340 --> 00:42:03,300
This depends on

1238
00:42:03,480 --> 00:42:05,350
where the scale of your love
is tipping toward.

1239
00:42:05,540 --> 00:42:07,260
Not giving birth is cheaper.

1240
00:42:11,180 --> 00:42:12,100
Let's go to the market.

1241
00:42:13,580 --> 00:42:14,980
There's a sale on eggs today.

1242
00:42:18,820 --> 00:42:19,900
You're so annoying.

1243
00:42:25,500 --> 00:42:26,180
Hello.

1244
00:42:26,180 --> 00:42:27,460
They found...

1245
00:42:27,780 --> 00:42:29,980
They found your younger sister!

1246
00:42:31,620 --> 00:42:32,780
She's in Guangzhou.

1247
00:42:33,180 --> 00:42:34,620
She'll come back tomorrow.

1248
00:42:36,500 --> 00:42:38,780
I gave her 3,000 yuan
in transportation fees.

1249
00:42:40,620 --> 00:42:41,540
Congratulations.

1250
00:42:41,820 --> 00:42:43,180
You've finally found a scammer.

1251
00:42:55,100 --> 00:42:56,950
The world is noisy

1252
00:42:57,550 --> 00:42:59,930
Turning around,
it's already a distant view

1253
00:43:01,350 --> 00:43:03,230
Once I didnt know what to do

1254
00:43:03,230 --> 00:43:05,310
What to hold quietly

1255
00:43:05,310 --> 00:43:08,260
Like a silent care

1256
00:43:10,120 --> 00:43:12,530
Seasons pass by

1257
00:43:12,530 --> 00:43:15,390
Time ticks away

1258
00:43:15,880 --> 00:43:17,790
Seems like I understand a little

1259
00:43:17,790 --> 00:43:19,570
And also let go of some things

1260
00:43:19,570 --> 00:43:24,290
All the bittersweet flavors
are the essence of youth

1261
00:43:24,290 --> 00:43:27,780
A long letter is written down

1262
00:43:27,930 --> 00:43:31,410
Gently spreading love

1263
00:43:31,610 --> 00:43:35,600
To all the forks in fate

1264
00:43:35,600 --> 00:43:41,230
Loving all the moments
that deserve to be loved
